H. perforatum ssp. veronense
( 10.4 mg g −1 D.W.) and the lowest in
H. empetrifolium ssp. empetrifolium
( 0.8 mg g −1 D.W.) ( Fig. 2 , Table 3 ). A myricetin hexoside ( 9 ), which has been reported in the genus (
), was detected and quantified herein in
H. empetrifolium ssp. empetrifolium
and
H. perfoliatum
